{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "鲁世雄在金国御林军统领完颜长之的府邸接受两场考试。第一场是上午与御林军十八名高手比武并大获全胜；第二场是在刀枪林立的威压下，为患病多年的祈参将施行开刀手术，将一个茶杯大的肉瘤割下，展现出精湛医术和过人胆识。完颜长之与御医对其大为赞赏，确认他是医隐德充符的弟子。考试结束后，鲁世雄被关入一间漆黑石牢，神秘蒙面人现身，自称是南宋临安派来的同僚，声称完颜长之已识破鲁世雄的奸细身份，要带他逃走。鲁世雄机警识破对方伪装，与其在黑牢中展开激战，一剑刺穿其面具——露出一个绝美少女的真面目。此时完颜长之推门而入，宣布最后一场考试已经结束。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_shi_A",
      "speaker_name": "卫士A",
      "listener": "char_wei_shi_B",
      "text": "咱们的王爷如此郑重其事倒是少见，你可知道这少年是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_shi_A",
      "speaker_name": "卫士A",
      "listener": "char_wei_shi_B",
      "text": "听说是济亲王檀元帅保举来的，名叫鲁世雄，是檀元帅一个老部下的儿子。檀元帅对他十分赏识。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_shi_B",
      "speaker_name": "卫士B",
      "listener": "char_wei_shi_A",
      "text": "哦，这就怪不得咱们的王爷对他如此看重了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_shi_A",
      "speaker_name": "卫士A",
      "listener": "char_wei_shi_B",
      "text": "不然，不然。檀元帅和咱们的王爷都是铁面无私的人，这个人若不是有真实的本领，咱们的王爷决不会任用，你瞧，现在不就是要他当众考试，以示无私吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_shi_B",
      "speaker_name": "卫士B",
      "listener": "char_wei_shi_A",
      "text": "考的什么试呀？为什么把患病多年的祈参将也抬了来？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_shi_A",
      "speaker_name": "卫士A",
      "listener": "char_wei_shi_B",
      "text": "这我就不知道了，不过，反正也就会揭晓了。噤声，噤声，王爷出来了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "御医",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "准备好了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi",
      "text": "准备好了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "你听清楚：他若死了，要你偿命！要是你不愿考试，现在还来得及！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "text": "我愿意接受这场考试。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，开刀！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_shi_mang",
      "speaker_name": "糊涂卫士",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "王爷说的，他若死了，要你偿命！你却胆敢把他杀了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
      "listener": "char_wei_shi_mang",
      "text": "蠢材，退下！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "御医",
      "listener": "char_zhu_shou",
      "text": "你们跟我这么多年，怎的还是如此糊涂，连真死假死都不知道？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_shou",
      "speaker_name": "助手",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi",
      "text": "他气息都没有了，还不是死么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "text": "王爷放心，他就会活过来的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi",
      "text": "他是任脉发病，故而小腹结块，现在我针他的太阳穴，不知对不对？",
      "tone": "谦逊",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "御医",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "你的医术很是不错，更难得的是如此镇定，真不愧是医隐德充符的弟子。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi",
      "text": "确是神乎其技。德充符的弟子尚且如此，德充符应该是天下第一了吧？何以有人说他还比不上柳元宗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "御医",
      "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "text": "因为柳元宗对穴道铜人的秘奥已懂得了一半。德充符只怕还是赶不上他的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
      "listener": "char_wei_shi_dui_zhang",
      "text": "上一场的武功考试，他的结果如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_shi_dui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "卫士队长",
      "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "text": "军中十八名高手，尽都败在他的手下。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "好，很好！你的武功医术都是上上之选，只要再通得过最后的一场考试，你就可以被录用了！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "text": "还有一场考试吗，不知考的什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "不错。这是最关紧要的一场考试！考的什么，何时举行，事前我都不能告诉你。或者是今天，或者是明天，或者是十天半月之后都说不定，好了，你考了两场，想必也很累了，你先去歇息吧。他的房间准备了没有？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_shi_dui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "卫士队长",
      "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "text": "准备好了。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
      "listener": "char_wei_shi_dui_zhang",
      "text": "好，你现在就陪他去吃饭，让他早点安歇。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_shi_dui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "卫士队长",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "我可是有点不懂，又不是要你当医官，为何要考你的医术？你可知道王爷要你做什么呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_wei_shi_dui_zhang",
      "text": "或者因为王爷知道我学过几年医，所以试试我的医术吧。只要能给王爷效劳，王爷任用我作什么，我都是高兴的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_shi_dui_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "卫士队长",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "就是这间房了，你早点安歇吧。养足精神，好好准备最后一场考试。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "咯伦科尔库钦哈已！咯伦科水库钦哈巴！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "你说什么？我听不懂！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "我说，你是奸细！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "我是来救你的！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "为什么说我是奸细？我和你到王爷跟前对质去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "哼，对质？是王爷叫我来拿你的！王爷早已知道你是奸细了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "你胡说八道，我不相信！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "哈哈，你不相信？你还在做着功名富贵的美梦？你想想看：你是檀元帅保荐来的人，如果不是因为王爷早已知道你是奸细，他焉会把你关进这个石牢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "你当真是奉命而来的吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "当然！要不然我怎进得了这个石牢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "好，那你就应该把我缚去呀，和我罗里罗唆地多说干什么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "你终于承认是奸细了吧。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "谁说我承认了，我一身清白，不怕旁人诬蔑。你马上带我去见王爷，我可以早些求个水落石出！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "蠢材呀，蠢材！你以为还可以蒙混得过吗？王爷早已掌握了证据，对你的底细知道得一清二楚了。你死不足惜，却误了大事了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "小声点儿。你不用害怕，我是来救你的！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "你究竟是什么人？我用不着你救！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "真人面前别说假话！到了现在你还和我装腔作势做什么？我和你一样，都是从江南来的。你混进了檀元帅的兵营，当了军官；我混进了完颜统领的王府，当了卫士。你明白了吧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "哦，原来你是临安的奸细！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "彼此彼此。幸亏今晚是差遣我来，否则你现在已经是身首异处了，闲话少说，赶快走吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拿奸细呀！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
      "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
      "text": "最后一场考试，已经完了！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1
    }
  ],
